  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 89.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第89课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "For Sale.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "待售。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Why couldn't Nigel decide?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "奈杰尔为什么拿不定主意？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Good afternoon.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "下午好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I believe that this house is for sale.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我听说这所房子要出售。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "That's right.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "是的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "May I have a look at it, please?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我可以看一看吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "当然可以。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Come in.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "请进。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "How long have you lived here?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "您在这里住了多久？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "I've lived here for twenty years.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我在这里住了二十年。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "Twenty years?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "二十年？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "That's a long time.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那可够久的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "Yes, I've been here since 1976.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "是的，我从1976年起就住在这里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "Then why do you want to sell it?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那您为什么想卖掉它？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "Because I've just retired.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "因为我刚退休。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "I want to buy a small house in the country.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我想在乡下买一所小房子。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "How much does this house cost?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这所房子多少钱？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "£68,500.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "68,500英镑。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "That's a lot of money.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那可是一大笔钱。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "text": "It's worth every penny of it.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "它值这个价，一分也不多。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "text": "Well, I like the house, but I can't decide yet.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "嗯，我喜欢这所房子，但还拿不定主意。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "text": "My wife must see it first.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我妻子必须先看看。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s025",
      "text": "Women always have the last word.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "女人总是最后说了算。"
      }
    }
  ],
